25/11/2010
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Police arrested a man on Wednesday (November 24th) on suspicion of planning to plant an explosive device at a bus station in Pale, Republika Srpska.
Kenan Suvalija, 36, was found in possession of firearms and items that could be used for making a bomb.
After detailed search at the bus station, the police found no explosive device.
An investigation is under way.
(Srna, RTRS, Nezavisne Novine - 24/11/10)
